@token = YOUR_BEARER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@bookingId = YOUR_BOOKING_UUID_HERE

### Create a Booking (Household Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "1",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-07-01T10:00:00Z",
  "price": 75.00
}

### Get All Bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Upcoming Bookings (Pending & Accepted)
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings?type=upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Completed Bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings?type=completed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Cancelled Bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/bookings?type=cancelled
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Accept a Booking (Worker Only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/bookings/{{bookingId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Complete a Booking (Worker Only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/bookings/{{bookingId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel a Booking (Household or Worker)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
